text: La Tina Ranch is a census-designated place (CDP) in Cameron County, in the U.S. state of Texas. The population was 618 at the 2010 census. Prior to the 2010 census the community was part of the Arroyo Gardens-La Tina Ranch CDP. It is part of the Brownsville-Harlingen Metropolitan Statistical Area. ==Geography== La Tina Ranch is in north-central Cameron County, east of Harlingen and north of Brownsville. It is bordered on the west by Arroyo Gardens.
